{"tid":501284,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"原創廣東歌Demo《來抱著入睡吧》","createTime":"2017-12-16T16:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T08:15:17.000Z","uid":131570,"like":85,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e946723c97eb54f9bf65107e00fd2aaaecef2d","tid":501284,"uid":131570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"大家好，我叫Hayne，啱啱畢業嘅大學生。<br />\n一直好鐘意音樂，由中學開始嘗試寫歌，但係寫咗好耐都冇成品。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到咗2017年，終於的起心肝寫，用咗3個月時間寫好呢首Demo。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於設備簡陋，所有嘢包括音樂底，聲，都係好raw好basic，所以叫raw take version。<br />\n但係我都想post咗個雛型俾大家，因為等咗太耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返首歌，其實特登想喺聖誕前後出，等我呢隻單身狗可以祝福一吓有另一半嘅巴打絲打可以有一個平安甜蜜嘅聖誕，喺寒冬可以抱著入睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n以下係Demo嘅Youtube Link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sFxF76hgCpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsFxF76hgCpI&d=GfjzNefjEofsLE8qdYCRNghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9facbd71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sFxF76hgCpI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首係我第一首曲詞編都自己試吓嘅作品，希望大家鐘意。我會繼續嘗試寫歌post上嚟㗎，多謝支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d4a0376949ec78d5a430acbfdc7af0bff41d79","tid":501284,"uid":131570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7e1036b813a4c6f85465ded9a9de9e7453f174a3","tid":501284,"uid":131570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c0a9682a004f7304f56a95ed83f71df2e4a9e1a","tid":501284,"uid":82779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"408aa347a5a1fc5399afa5b0431c58451b03ec81","tid":50128